<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8" ?>
<Defs>
	
	<HediffDef ParentName="EVOR_Hediff_BodyPartBase_18PartEfficiency">
		<defName>EVOR_Hediff_Eye</defName>
		<label>multispectrum eye</label>
		<labelNoun>a multispectrum eye</labelNoun>
		<spawnThingOnRemoved>EVOR_Item_Eye</spawnThingOnRemoved>
		<stages>
			<li>
				<statOffsets>
					<AimingDelayFactor>-0.10</AimingDelayFactor>
					<ShootingAccuracyPawn>2</ShootingAccuracyPawn>
				</statOffsets>
			</li>
		</stages>
    <description>By integrating cells that allow for collection of light in the ultraviolent and infrared spectrum, these eyes allow for much more spacial awareness of their host.</description>
		<descriptionHyperlinks><ThingDef>EVOR_Item_Eye</ThingDef></descriptionHyperlinks>
	</HediffDef>
	
	<HediffDef ParentName="EVOR_Hediff_BodyPartBase_18PartEfficiency">
		<defName>EVOR_Hediff_Nose</defName>
		<label>micro-analyzer nose</label>
		<labelNoun>a micro-analyzer nose</labelNoun>
		<spawnThingOnRemoved>EVOR_Item_Nose</spawnThingOnRemoved>
		<stages>
			<li>
				<statOffsets>
					<PlantWorkSpeed>0.3</PlantWorkSpeed>
					<TameAnimalChance>0.2</TameAnimalChance>
					<TrainAnimalChance>0.4</TrainAnimalChance>
				</statOffsets>
			</li>
		</stages>
    <description>Increasing the amount of cells dedicated to analyzing specific molecules, certain scents can be more easily distinguished from surrounding gasses.</description>
		<descriptionHyperlinks><ThingDef>EVOR_Item_Nose</ThingDef></descriptionHyperlinks>
	</HediffDef>
	
	<HediffDef ParentName="EVOR_Hediff_BodyPartBase_18PartEfficiency">
		<defName>EVOR_Hediff_Nose_Pheromones</defName>
		<label>pheromone releaser nose</label>
		<labelNoun>a pheromone releaser nose</labelNoun>
		<spawnThingOnRemoved>EVOR_Item_Nose_Pheromones</spawnThingOnRemoved>
		<stages>
			<li>
				<statOffsets>
					<NegotiationAbility>0.3</NegotiationAbility>
					<TradePriceImprovement>0.2</TradePriceImprovement>
					<SocialImpact>0.4</SocialImpact>
				</statOffsets>
			</li>
		</stages>
    <description>By adding special pheromone glands to the base of the nose, the host can slightly alter the disposition of those they are communicating with.</description>
		<descriptionHyperlinks><ThingDef>EVOR_Item_Nose_Pheromones</ThingDef></descriptionHyperlinks>
	</HediffDef>
	
	<HediffDef ParentName="EVOR_Hediff_BodyPartBase_18PartEfficiency">
		<defName>EVOR_Hediff_Ear</defName>
		<label>multifrequency ear</label>
		<labelNoun>a multifrequency ear</labelNoun>
		<spawnThingOnRemoved>EVOR_Item_Ear</spawnThingOnRemoved>
		<stages>
			<li>
				<statOffsets>
					<MeleeDodgeChance>2</MeleeDodgeChance>
				</statOffsets>
			</li>
		</stages>
    <description>By increasing the spectrum of frequencies able to be picked up, as well as allowing the host to temporarily focus on one frequency, these ears allows the host to percieve all sounds in the vicinity.</description>
		<descriptionHyperlinks><ThingDef>EVOR_Item_Ear</ThingDef></descriptionHyperlinks>
	</HediffDef>
	
	<HediffDef ParentName="EVOR_Hediff_BodyPartBase_18PartEfficiency">
		<defName>EVOR_Hediff_Jaw_Distend</defName>
		<label>distendable jaw</label>
		<labelNoun>a distendable jaw</labelNoun>
		<spawnThingOnRemoved>EVOR_Item_Jaw_Distend</spawnThingOnRemoved>
		<stages>
			<li>
                <statOffsets>
          			<EatingSpeed>0.7</EatingSpeed>
          			<SocialImpact>0.05</SocialImpact>
        		</statOffsets>
            </li>
		</stages>
		<comps>
			<li Class="HediffCompProperties_VerbGiver">
				<tools>
					<li>
						<capacities>
							<li>Stab</li>
						</capacities>
						<power>10.0</power>
						<cooldownTime>2.7</cooldownTime>
					</li>
				</tools>
			</li>
		</comps>
    <description>By allowing the jaw to detach from the skull while still delivering a powerful bite, this jaw allows the host to consume food at a rapid rate.</description>
		<descriptionHyperlinks><ThingDef>EVOR_Item_Jaw_Distend</ThingDef></descriptionHyperlinks>
	</HediffDef>
	
	<HediffDef ParentName="EVOR_Hediff_BodyPartBase_10PartEfficiency">
		<defName>EVOR_Hediff_Jaw_Venom</defName>
		<label>venomous fangs</label>
		<labelNoun>venomous fangs</labelNoun>
		<spawnThingOnRemoved>EVOR_Item_Jaw_Venom</spawnThingOnRemoved>
		<comps>
			<li Class="HediffCompProperties_VerbGiver">
				<tools>
					<li>
						<capacities>
							<li>EVOR_Cap_Toxic</li>
						</capacities>
						<power>17.0</power>
						<cooldownTime>2.7</cooldownTime>
						<alwaysTreatAsWeapon>true</alwaysTreatAsWeapon>
					</li>
				</tools>
			</li>
		</comps>
    <description>By producing a deadly venom and injecting it into the enemy, the host has a hidden weapon available in all situations.</description>
		<descriptionHyperlinks><ThingDef>EVOR_Item_Jaw_Venom</ThingDef></descriptionHyperlinks>
	</HediffDef>
	
	
	
	
</Defs>